# Modern browsers only - no legacy support
# This reduces polyfills for features like Array.prototype.at, Object.fromEntries, etc.
# These features are natively supported in:
# - Chrome 92+ (July 2021)
# - Firefox 90+ (July 2021)
# - Safari 15.4+ (March 2022)
# - Edge 92+ (July 2021)

# Target modern browsers (last 2 versions of major browsers)
last 2 Chrome versions
last 2 Firefox versions
last 2 Safari versions
last 2 Edge versions

# Exclude very old browsers
not dead
not IE 11

# Mobile browsers
last 2 iOS versions
last 2 ChromeAndroid versions
